okapi.metadata.MetadataRequest.name: MetadataRequest
okapi.metadata.MetadataRequest.description:
Request custom metadata about the native okapi binaries - cannot get cargo env vars at runtime

repeated string variables = 1; // optional field, can contain any of the cargo env vars

okapi.metadata.MetadataResponse.description: Metadata information about the native okapi binaries. Always returns the version information
